<br>
Also heading down east hallway the big room has SK centis that will almost always HT for 500+.  The centi in the east room straight against the wall is an enchanter (and light blue).  It will try to charm, mez, etc.  Not too tough, just have to be careful and keep HP and resists high on pulling the east room.<br>
