<br>
Then i went to katta bank.  i was able to pull the entire bank, and 4-6 guards from the tunnel non stop.  I was getting over 10% an hour.  I do not have fancy gear at all.  No FT items.  And just last night purchased a burnt wood staff.    <br>
<br>
If you have some good gear, you probably could get more out of Akevea than i did.  But for a low  equiped non epic mage, I think katta is the way to go.  almost no risk if you play it right. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#333333>- </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>The Magician's Tower</a><font color=#333333> - </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24>Levels 56-60</a> <font color=#333333> - </font><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/">The Mage Compendium</a><font color=#333333> - </font>  <br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
